item.title: Grad Weekend Fall 21
item.description: The RCAF and Delta Phi of Alpha Chi Rho Building Association successfully hosted the bi-annual Grad Weekend, both virtually and in-person. The General Meeting was held from 10:30AM-12:30 PM Sunday morning with 25 members in attendance. The meeting minutes have been uploaded to the google drive.
